  <source>Hospital Moinhos de Vento</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effectiveness of pharmaceutical care, compared
      to usual care, in improving medication adherence behaviour of ambulatory hemodialysis
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
